{"type": "article", "id": 24825, "title": "麻将沙发", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-01T06:54:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160608131022NwAtT9EiMgzaOfJ6.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一套模块化的沙发，也是法国家居品牌 Roche Bobois 的一款经典产品。带靠背的坐垫和无靠背的坐垫都在方形的模块里，可以自由移动拼接组成一组长沙发或沙发床，也很方便叠起来收纳。今年 Roche Bobois 邀请了 8 位艺术家设计新的拼接图案，让这种形式自由的沙发有更多的选择，符合其自由的个性。<br></p>\n<div class=\"medium-insert-active com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131019e5qrD0LCsvxIizYE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49679487\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131020FBCT0iw2vrjW7yJl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 411px; width: 375px; left: 478px; top: 1261px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131020MvHYslFRiWxUgbIf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09508547\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131021zbBr4ucKXGwevW3T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74465812\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160608131021gpmrswRFHoa18jBG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64316239\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}